ot have put this comment in the book. Also, there is a theme throughout the book about her wanting to disappear or be invisible. Despite this she still tells us how she would dress in colourful clothes and low cut tops. Of course she has been mentally damaged by her past and I do feel for all of the children who endured what she did and far worse. But I get a sense of this woman capitalising on her past in a way which I find a little irritating. I also think the family who kept taking them into their home were not given as much attention as they deserved. We are told, Manuella, the lovely daughter of this family had died. The author idolised this young woman but all we are told is that she is dead. I wanted to know more about her and how she came to die. I was also surprised to learn that the picture of the little girl in the red coat was not in fact the author - she just 'recognised' herself in her. I imagine so did many many other children. \u003cbr /\u003e","rating":2,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4118002?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/246204050"},"likeCount":16,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":3,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1._1tx1284C5MV5Nnzf-p5SQ":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1._1tx1284C5MV5Nnzf-p5SQ","__typename":"Book"},"User:6181069":{"id":6181069,"__typename":"User","legacyId":6181069,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1547371456i/6181069._UX200_CR0,38,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":1005,"viewableName":"Ingrid","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/6181069-ingrid","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":0},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.fcCoOawSgucf1CPALI7sUQ":{"id":"kca://review:goodre