iptive writing. I never felt like I was with her in the moment. I coulnd't imagine what the scenes looked like, or what he life really felt like, especially earlier on.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e3. The way she reminisces about her mother is on-point, and the flow of their relationship is handled extremely well. There were some moments where you could really feel all the feelings. That was excellent.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e4. Yeah. It's hard to rate a memoir, as I sort of feel like I'm giving critique on a person's life. But from what I read about her elsewhere, I think this book could have been revised a few more times to make more connection with the readers.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eRating: 3 stars out of 5","rating":3,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/15234560?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1157428925"},"likeCount":5,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":1,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"User:14876131":{"id":14876131,"__typename":"User","legacyId":14876131,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1584831978i/14876131._UX200_CR0,0,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":87,"viewableName":"Kate Hamlet","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/14876131-kate-hamlet","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":0},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.p2pMKWp_Bm034N8zJ0IVPw":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.p2pMKWp_Bm034N8zJ0IVPw","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.Mx8kZJBNxldDo3wz8v-sBQ"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:14876131"},"recommendFor":null,"updatedAt":1554741045247,"createdAt":1420119777000,"spoilerStatus":false,"lastRevisionAt":1436658382000,"text":"I really felt that this could have bee